      <li><a href="/outdoor/grill-repair/">Outdoor grill repair</a></li>
      <li><a href="/outdoor/kitchen-repair/">Outdoor kitchen repair</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bottom-cta">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Solaira Down? Call Today.</h2>
    <p>Same-day across LA, OC, Ventura. $120 outdoor diagnostic waived with repair. BHGS #A49573, EPA 608 Universal #1346255700410. IP65 weather-rated unit specialists.</p>
    <div class="cta-row">
      <a href={phoneHref} class="btn-primary">☎ Call {phone}</a>
